videos.headline: Burrow finds Chase for 1st TD of day
videos.description: Joe Burrow throws a 37-yard lob to Ja'Marr Chase who hauls it in for the first touchdown of the day early in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow finds Chase for 1st TD of day) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Davis-Price powers in for TD
videos.description: Tyrion Davis-Price makes easy work of the two-yard touchdown run to extend No. 1 LSU's lead over Arkansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Davis-Price powers in for TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shaq lifts cheerleaders during break
videos.description: Shaquille O'Neal lifts cheerleaders for a picture during the commercial break of the LSU-Arkansas football game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Shaq lifts cheerleaders during break) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Edwards-Helaire takes off for 27-yard TD
videos.description: Clyde Edwards-Helaire goes 27 yards untouched as No. 1 LSU keeps piling on touchdowns over Arkansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Edwards-Helaire takes off for 27-yard TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chase walks in unscathed for 50-yard LSU TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow finds Ja'Marr Chase without a defender close to him as Chase walks into the end zone untouched for a 50-yard LSU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Chase walks in unscathed for 50-yard LSU TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Orgeron: No reason to celebrate beating Arkansas
videos.description: Ed Orgeron says there's no reason for No. 1 LSU to celebrate after beating Arkansas, as Arkansas hasn't beaten anyone in a long time.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Orgeron: No reason to celebrate beating Arkansas) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: LSU shows off balanced attack in rout of Arkansas
videos.description: LSU clinches a birth in the SEC championship behind another strong performance from Joe Burrow and Clyde Edwards-Helaire's three rushing touchdowns.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Feature (LSU shows off balanced attack in rout of Arkansas) 2019/11/19 ESHEET ENHL
